Company : Chameleon Digital Media
E-Mail  : cameleon@magnet.ca

A one hour video tape which teaches young children how to create sculptures
from recycled newspapers and magazines. The technique is being promoted in
Quebec as a replacement for papermarcher. The only materials needed are
newspaper and rubber bands.  The first step one learns is how to create a
